from each other.

00:33:10.760 --> 00:33:14.110
And in Breath of Life
we take participants

00:33:14.110 --> 00:33:15.410
with different backgrounds.

00:33:15.410 --> 00:33:19.180
We might have someone coming
in who has been involved

00:33:19.180 --> 00:33:24.300
