00:33:53.860 --> 00:33:55.580
Now I know people who
have been doing it

00:33:55.580 --> 00:33:59.060
and who are willing to advise me.

00:33:59.060 --> 00:34:02.970
So, yeah, there's very
much a lot of communication

00:34:02.970 --> 00:34:06.370
and we try to foster that as well.

