of educational practices grounded

01:00:06.230 --> 01:00:10.550 position:56%
on the notion that people;
children can only learn one language

01:00:10.550 --> 01:00:13.730
and if they learn two or
more, they'll be delayed.

01:00:13.730 --> 01:00:16.140
They'll go crazy, etcetera.

01:00:16.140 --> 01:00:18.850
So, now, we're in a different
situation where we have

01:00:18.850 --> 01:00:26.840
