that a child not only can earn more

01:00:26.840 --> 01:00:33.490
than a language, but that the child
will develop certain abilities

01:00:33.490 --> 01:00:38.330 position:56%
beyond the levels that a monolingual
child will be able to develop them.

01:00:38.330 --> 01:00:40.660
And these are abilities
like executive function.

01:00:40.660 --> 01:00:42.970
The ability to focus on
one thing despite the fact

01:00:42.970 --> 01:00:46.160
that we might have a lot
of stimuli around you.

01:00:46.160 --> 01:00:49.600
That is much more developed
in a bilingual child

01:00:49.600 --> 01:00:52.070
than in a monolingual child.

01:00:52.070 --> 01:00:54.070
So, we can start pushing that out

01:00:54.070 --> 01:00:57.660
